#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Cold_00"
msgid ""
"Freezing Climates<1.ra>Wear cold-resistant clothing or eat something that"
" warms your body\n"
"when adventuring in cold regions. Otherwise, the cold will slowly\n"
"chip away at your health."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Enemy_00"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>It's dangerous to approach enemies head-on when you're "
"low on\n"
"hearts or don't have protective armor equipped. Always be prepared!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Enemy_01"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Instead of throwing yourself at enemies over and over to "
"no avail,\n"
"try cooking special dishes and elixirs to give yourself better defense,\n"
"extra damage, or more hearts."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Fall_00"
msgid ""
"Falling Death<1.ra>Depending on the height, you may take damage, or even "
"die, when\n"
"you fall. So be cautious out there walking near cliff edges!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Fall_01"
msgid ""
"Falling Death<1.ra>Depending on the height, you may take damage, or even "
"die, when\n"
"you fall. Remember to use the paraglider for a safe descent."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Guardian_00"
msgid ""
"Guardians<1.ra>Their entire bodies are covered in armor, so low-powered "
"weapons\n"
"won't do any damage. It's best to avoid these foes until you have\n"
"the right tools for the job!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Lightning_00"
msgid ""
"Lightning Strikes<1.ra>It may sound like a superstition, but lightning "
"seems to strike metal\n"
"objects frequently. If you hear thunder, unequip anything metallic."
msgstr ""

